    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and fading on the hood, while the interior has some wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for functional transportation at a reasonable price.",
